Bordersize (GUI item property)
==============================

The stroke size, in relative pixels, of the item border. The border is created to the inside of the item, and its color can be set by using the [bordercolor](Bordercolor\_(GUI\_item\_property)) property.

The value of this property cannot be changed at runtime.

Syntax
------

`bordersize `*`size`*

Default value
-------------

`0`

Example(s)
----------

`bordersize 1`

